    <div class=\"access-header\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined access-icon\">lock_open</span>\n        <h1>Solicitar acceso</h1>\n        <p>Esta plataforma es privada y el acceso es solo por invitación.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"access-body\">\n        <h2>¿Cómo funciona?</h2>\n        <ol class=\"access-steps\">\n          <li>\n            <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined step-icon\">edit_note</span>\n            <div>\n              <strong>Abre una solicitud en GitHub</strong>\n              <p>Crea una issue indicando quién eres y qué curso te interesa. No necesitas cuenta técnica, solo un usuario de GitHub.</p>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined step-icon\">schedule</span>\n            <div>\n              <strong>Revisión personal</strong>\n              <p>Reviso cada solicitud manualmente. Si encajas, te envío una invitación por email.</p>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined step-icon\">celebration</span>\n            <div>\n              <strong>Accedes a la plataforma</strong>\n              <p>Con tu cuenta de Google podrás entrar y acceder a los cursos asignados.</p>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/manufosela/manuelearning/issues/new?title=Solicitud+de+acceso&body=Hola+Mánu%2C%0A%0AMe+gustaría+acceder+a+la+plataforma.%0A%0A**Nombre**%3A+%0A**Curso+que+me+interesa**%3A+%0A**Cómo+te+conozco**%3A+%0A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"btn btn--primary btn--lg access-btn\">\n          Abrir solicitud en GitHub\n        </a>\n\n        <div class=\"access-alt\">\n          <p>¿No tienes GitHub? Escríbeme directamente a <a href=\"mailto:manufosela@gmail.com?subject=Solicitud%20de%20acceso%20ManuElearning\">manufosela@gmail.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</MainLayout>\n\n<style>\n  .access-page {\n    min-height: 80vh;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    padding: 2rem var(--section-px);\n  }\n\n  .access-card {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);\n    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);\n    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);\n    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-icon {\n    font-size: 2.5rem;\n    color: var(--color-primary);\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-header h1 {\n    font-size: 1.75rem;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-header p {\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    font-size: 0.938rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-body h2 {\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-steps {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 1.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    counter-reset: step;\n  }\n\n  .access-steps li {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n  }\n\n  .step-icon {\n    color: var(--color-primary);\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    margin-top: 0.125rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-steps li strong {\n    display: block;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-steps li p {\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n\n  .access-btn {\n    width: 100%;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-alt {\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .access-alt p {\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    font-size: 0.813rem;\n  }\n\n  .access-alt a {\n    color: var(--color-primary);\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n\n  .access-alt a:hover {\n    text-decoration: underline;\n  }\n</style>\n","numLines":157,"startLine":1,"totalLines":157}}} (stream=stdout)
